# All ViteRex paths and settings live in the Redaxo backend
# (AddOns → ViteRex → Settings), persisted to `rex_config` and synced to
# `var/data/addons/viterex/structure.json` for the Vite plugin to read.
#
# This file exists only as a starting point if your project also needs
# Vite-specific env vars (loaded by Vite via `loadEnv`). ViteRex itself
# reads no env vars on the PHP side — leave this file empty unless you
# add your own.
